1
00:07:24,010 --> 00:07:25,140
<font color="yellow">He's a new face.</font>

2
00:07:25,140 --> 00:07:28,710
<font color="yellow">He's the one who has been roaming about for a long time.</font>

3
00:07:28,710 --> 00:07:30,240
<font color="yellow">Oh, that one.</font>

4
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,640
<font color="yellow">20 years ago,</font>

5
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:34,240
<font color="yellow">he even escaped from a grim reaper after confronting one.</font>

6
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,870
<font color="yellow">I think it's been about 20 years.</font>

7
00:07:36,710 --> 00:07:38,740
<font color="yellow">I came across a deceased soul...</font>

8
00:07:38,940 --> 00:07:41,070
<font color="yellow">and I had no information on it.</font>

9
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:44,040
<font color="yellow">Really? I had a similar experience when I was nine...</font>

10
00:07:44,210 --> 00:07:46,710
<font color="yellow">It seemed like it had been roaming about for a long time.</font>

11
00:07:47,140 --> 00:07:48,970
<font color="yellow">It seemed fearless.</font>

12
00:07:50,710 --> 00:07:53,770
<font color="yellow">I never saw a deceased soul who didn't fear a grim reaper.</font>

13
00:07:53,770 --> 00:07:55,040
<font color="yellow">I thought it was strange.</font>

14
00:08:51,610 --> 00:08:52,910
<font color="yellow">Nice to meet you.</font>

15
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,780
<font color="yellow">So you are the goblin's bride.</font>

16
00:09:15,870 --> 00:09:18,280
<font color="yellow">Yes, same here.</font>

17
00:09:18,670 --> 00:09:23,010
<font color="yellow">You shouldn't make yourselves at home in someone's place of business.</font>

18
00:09:23,010 --> 00:09:25,610
<font color="yellow">You'll keep the customers from coming.</font>

19
00:09:25,810 --> 00:09:27,840
<font color="yellow">It's time to do business, so please leave.</font>

20
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,070
<font color="yellow">Cold-hearted brat.</font>

21
00:09:29,070 --> 00:09:31,340
<font color="yellow">You first. Hurry.</font>

22
00:09:31,340 --> 00:09:33,110
<font color="yellow">Unfriendly brat!</font>

23
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:18,870
<font color="yellow">He felt...</font>

24
00:10:20,570 --> 00:10:22,640
<font color="yellow">In my 20 years of seeing ghosts,</font>

25
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:24,970
<font color="yellow">I've never seen anything like it.</font>

26
00:10:27,710 --> 00:10:29,040
<font color="yellow">Let's forget.</font>

27
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:32,070
<font color="yellow">I'm too busy to think about ghosts.</font>

28
00:10:33,710 --> 00:10:37,070
<font color="yellow">If I take all the classes within four days,</font>

29
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:40,440
<font color="yellow">I'll have to start work later.</font>

30
00:10:42,610 --> 00:10:43,670
<font color="yellow">Like this?</font>

31
00:10:49,210 --> 00:10:52,370
<font color="yellow">A love letter? You're so annoying.</font>

32
00:10:52,370 --> 00:10:55,770
<font color="yellow">I'm too busy just trying to survive, and you wrote a love letter?</font>

33
00:11:09,770 --> 00:11:10,870
<font color="yellow">I am...</font>

34
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:14,640
<font color="yellow">a grim reaper.</font>

35
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:22,440
<font color="yellow">I want to see him.</font>

36
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:29,170
<font color="yellow">I don't want to see him.</font>

37
00:11:29,870 --> 00:11:32,040
<font color="yellow">I want to see him.</font>

38
00:11:37,040 --> 00:11:40,570
<font color="yellow">How is it always exactly seven shots?</font>

39
00:11:42,940 --> 00:11:47,370
<font color="yellow">I know it'll end exactly after seven shots,</font>

40
00:11:47,370 --> 00:11:49,940
<font color="yellow">but started with "I want to see him."</font>

41
00:11:53,870 --> 00:11:55,910
<font color="yellow">I want to see him.</font>

42
00:11:56,210 --> 00:11:57,970
<font color="yellow">I don't want to see him.</font>

43
00:11:57,970 --> 00:12:00,510
<font color="yellow">I want to see him.</font>

44
00:12:04,010 --> 00:12:07,510
<font color="yellow">Have you ever been hit by peach flowers?</font>

45
00:12:07,510 --> 00:12:08,770
<font color="yellow">I have.</font>

46
00:12:08,940 --> 00:12:11,210
<font color="yellow">I got a beating at a shaman's house.</font>

47
00:12:11,310 --> 00:12:13,010
<font color="yellow">That scars for a while.</font>

48
00:12:14,870 --> 00:12:16,240
<font color="yellow">The previous ones were better.</font>

49
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:18,340
<font color="yellow">Right? They were, right?</font>

50
00:12:19,670 --> 00:12:20,840
<font color="yellow">Have you...</font>

51
00:12:21,770 --> 00:12:24,770
<font color="yellow">ever wanted to get your memory back?</font>

52
00:12:27,210 --> 00:12:28,410
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

53
00:12:29,370 --> 00:12:31,010
<font color="yellow">What is a memory you've forgotten?</font>

54
00:12:31,010 --> 00:12:33,070
<font color="yellow">It's like a memory that you never had.</font>

55
00:12:33,210 --> 00:12:35,340
<font color="yellow">You never had it anyway, so why?</font>

56
00:12:50,810 --> 00:12:51,910
<font color="yellow">I...</font>

57
00:12:53,410 --> 00:12:54,940
<font color="yellow">miss it.</font>

58
00:12:55,010 --> 00:12:56,340
<font color="yellow">Don't.</font>

59
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,470
<font color="yellow">We are all sinners.</font>

60
00:12:59,340 --> 00:13:01,870
<font color="yellow">We don't know what that longing will bring.</font>

61
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:03,310
<font color="yellow">I know.</font>

62
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:06,040
<font color="yellow">I know it.</font>

63
00:13:08,070 --> 00:13:10,710
<font color="yellow">Each time I long for it,</font>

64
00:13:11,270 --> 00:13:12,970
<font color="yellow">I don't know where it's going to take me,</font>

65
00:13:12,970 --> 00:13:14,670
<font color="yellow">and it dreads me.</font>

66
00:13:18,470 --> 00:13:19,470
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

67
00:13:21,640 --> 00:13:23,710
<font color="yellow">I still miss it.</font>

68
00:13:38,410 --> 00:13:40,940
<font color="yellow">It looks like you're drinking too much today.</font>

69
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:46,540
<font color="yellow">I got caught. Sunny found out that I am a grim reaper.</font>

70
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:49,510
<font color="yellow">Good job.</font>

71
00:13:50,070 --> 00:13:51,640
<font color="yellow">Where did she get...</font>

72
00:13:51,970 --> 00:13:55,140
<font color="yellow">a branch of peach flowers in the middle of winter?</font>

73
00:14:01,770 --> 00:14:02,840
<font color="yellow">Exactly.</font>

74
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,340
<font color="yellow">What do I do now?</font>

75
00:14:04,970 --> 00:14:06,540
<font color="yellow">She must be very confused.</font>

76
00:14:06,540 --> 00:14:07,770
<font color="yellow">What are you worried about?</font>

77
00:14:07,770 --> 00:14:09,740
<font color="yellow">Since you already got caught, you should hold her hands.</font>

78
00:14:09,740 --> 00:14:11,140
<font color="yellow">And see if you see my face.</font>

79
00:14:12,610 --> 00:14:13,710
<font color="yellow">I said I got caught.</font>

80
00:14:13,710 --> 00:14:16,440
<font color="yellow">So casually hold her hand and see if you see me.</font>

81
00:14:16,610 --> 00:14:18,040
<font color="yellow">You are greatly mistaken.</font>

82
00:14:18,040 --> 00:14:19,540
<font color="yellow">Do you know how hard it is to see one's past life?</font>

83
00:14:19,540 --> 00:14:23,070
<font color="yellow">It comes to you as if someone is suddenly pushing it inside you.</font>

84
00:14:23,870 --> 00:14:27,270
<font color="yellow">When the lady in the picture came to life, she was so beautiful.</font>

85
00:14:27,270 --> 00:14:28,770
<font color="yellow">And her beauty totally made me go mad.</font>

86
00:14:31,740 --> 00:14:33,040
<font color="yellow">She's my sister.</font>

87
00:14:33,410 --> 00:14:34,710
<font color="yellow">So...</font>

88
00:14:35,910 --> 00:14:38,710
<font color="yellow">I did see one young and foolish face.</font>

89
00:14:38,710 --> 00:14:39,870
<font color="yellow">It was that young king.</font>

90
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:42,440
<font color="yellow">My foolish sister must've only thought about him.</font>

91
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:44,270
<font color="yellow">She doesn't care about her brother at all.</font>

92
00:14:47,770 --> 00:14:49,970
<font color="yellow">I'm here. What is it?</font>

93
00:14:51,010 --> 00:14:53,170
<font color="yellow">It's nothing. I'll come next time.</font>

94
00:14:55,340 --> 00:14:58,240
<font color="yellow">Give it to me. Don't look at my notebook.</font>

95
00:14:58,240 --> 00:15:00,540
<font color="yellow">Why did you write about me then?</font>

96
00:15:02,170 --> 00:15:03,170
<font color="yellow">What is this?</font>

97
00:15:03,170 --> 00:15:05,170
<font color="yellow">Did you forge a document again behind my back?</font>

98
00:15:05,770 --> 00:15:07,340
<font color="yellow">Stop pretending not to know what it is.</font>

99
00:15:07,340 --> 00:15:10,040
<font color="yellow">It's a love letter. It's a love letter you wrote.</font>

100
00:15:10,040 --> 00:15:11,370
<font color="yellow">Did he write a love letter?</font>

101
00:15:11,770 --> 00:15:13,740
<font color="yellow">He did for his first love.</font>

102
00:15:13,740 --> 00:15:17,340
<font color="yellow">I wanted to know how it ended and see how special it was.</font>

103
00:15:17,340 --> 00:15:19,870
<font color="yellow">I was going to ask for your help.</font>

104
00:15:20,170 --> 00:15:22,610
<font color="yellow">Do you know what it's about? It's not a love letter.</font>

105
00:15:22,610 --> 00:15:23,940
<font color="yellow">Whatever.</font>

106
00:15:23,940 --> 00:15:25,770
<font color="yellow">It was very well-written.</font>

107
00:15:26,040 --> 00:15:28,070
<font color="yellow">"One day after 100 years..."</font>

108
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:30,870
<font color="yellow">"When the weather is good enough."</font>

109
00:15:31,070 --> 00:15:32,970
<font color="yellow">- That's not it. - That is it.</font>

110
00:15:32,970 --> 00:15:34,910
<font color="yellow">Deok Hwa read everything to me.</font>

111
00:15:34,910 --> 00:15:37,240
<font color="yellow">"One day after 100 years..."</font>

112
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:40,040
<font color="yellow">"When the weather is good enough."</font>

113
00:15:40,040 --> 00:15:41,140
<font color="yellow">That's impossible.</font>

114
00:15:41,140 --> 00:15:43,640
<font color="yellow">Deok Hwa could never read this.</font>

115
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:45,240
<font color="yellow">That wasn't written anywhere.</font>

116
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:47,040
<font color="yellow">I've been keeping it to myself.</font>

117
00:15:47,040 --> 00:15:49,070
<font color="yellow">One day after 100 years...</font>

118
00:15:49,810 --> 00:15:51,840
<font color="yellow">When the weather is good enough,</font>

119
00:15:52,540 --> 00:15:54,210
<font color="yellow">I hope I'll be able to...</font>

120
00:15:54,610 --> 00:15:56,110
<font color="yellow">tell her she was my first love.</font>

121
00:15:57,010 --> 00:15:59,740
<font color="yellow">Right. That's not it.</font>

122
00:16:01,510 --> 00:16:02,710
<font color="yellow">That can't be right.</font>

123
00:16:02,710 --> 00:16:05,170
<font color="yellow">Deok Hwa interpreted it for me.</font>

124
00:16:05,170 --> 00:16:06,240
<font color="yellow">It's a love letter.</font>

125
00:16:08,010 --> 00:16:09,140
<font color="yellow">When...</font>

126
00:16:10,140 --> 00:16:12,010
<font color="yellow">you blew away tens of cars,</font>

127
00:16:12,010 --> 00:16:13,510
<font color="yellow">did you tell Deok Hwa...</font>

128
00:16:13,770 --> 00:16:16,410
<font color="yellow">that I could help people forget?</font>

129
00:16:16,640 --> 00:16:17,640
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

130
00:16:17,640 --> 00:16:19,540
<font color="yellow">Come with me.</font>

131
00:16:19,610 --> 00:16:21,710
<font color="yellow">How did he know and...</font>

132
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:24,310
<font color="yellow">ask me to come along?</font>

133
00:16:26,010 --> 00:16:27,470
<font color="yellow">Actually,</font>

134
00:16:27,710 --> 00:16:31,010
<font color="yellow">Deok Hwa found me the maple leaf.</font>

135
00:16:31,010 --> 00:16:32,870
<font color="yellow">I had lost it.</font>

136
00:16:33,270 --> 00:16:35,810
<font color="yellow">Guess where this leaf is from.</font>

137
00:16:36,340 --> 00:16:37,470
<font color="yellow">What's going on?</font>

138
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:45,940
<font color="yellow">That's impressive.</font>

139
00:16:48,870 --> 00:16:50,210
<font color="yellow">Why didn't I realize sooner?</font>

140
00:16:51,770 --> 00:16:56,140
<font color="yellow">He even dared to put the goblin's house in the market.</font>

141
00:17:12,510 --> 00:17:15,770
<font color="yellow">I don't know if it was the king, the divinity, or me.</font>

142
00:17:19,170 --> 00:17:21,110
<font color="yellow">This letter means "to hear".</font>

143
00:17:23,010 --> 00:17:25,410
<font color="yellow">I found her, She's at the ski resort right now.</font>

144
00:17:25,840 --> 00:17:29,240
<font color="yellow">That's because your boss was his sister in their past lives.</font>

145
00:17:30,070 --> 00:17:31,110
<font color="yellow">Shall we...</font>

146
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:34,170
<font color="yellow">have a drink?</font>

147
00:17:34,170 --> 00:17:38,370
<font color="yellow">Finally, the goblin met the goblin's bride.</font>

148
00:17:38,540 --> 00:17:39,840
<font color="yellow">It's a destiny.</font>

149
00:17:42,170 --> 00:17:43,610
<font color="yellow">What about Yeo?</font>

150
00:17:44,540 --> 00:17:46,410
<font color="yellow">How could you make them meet?</font>

151
00:17:46,410 --> 00:17:48,810
<font color="yellow">One with a sword in his chest and the man who did it to him.</font>

152
00:17:48,810 --> 00:17:50,140
<font color="yellow">What brings you to my house?</font>

153
00:17:50,140 --> 00:17:51,140
<font color="yellow">Do you live here?</font>

154
00:17:51,140 --> 00:17:53,010
<font color="yellow">That's a destiny too.</font>

155
00:17:54,170 --> 00:17:55,510
<font color="yellow">He was looking for a house anyway.</font>

156
00:17:55,510 --> 00:17:57,240
<font color="yellow">You need to take down a notch.</font>

157
00:17:57,240 --> 00:17:58,910
<font color="yellow">What on earth are you thinking?</font>

158
00:17:59,170 --> 00:18:00,770
<font color="yellow">I love him particularly.</font>

159
00:18:00,770 --> 00:18:03,540
<font color="yellow">It's been 900 years since Kim Shin has been punished.</font>

160
00:18:03,540 --> 00:18:04,540
<font color="yellow">Is that still not enough?</font>

161
00:18:04,540 --> 00:18:07,040
<font color="yellow">That's how substantial one's life is.</font>

162
00:18:22,170 --> 00:18:23,910
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you create a perfect world...</font>

163
00:18:23,910 --> 00:18:25,810
<font color="yellow">without a sin in the first place?</font>

164
00:18:25,810 --> 00:18:27,410
<font color="yellow">Then nobody would look for the almighty.</font>

165
00:18:28,040 --> 00:18:30,170
<font color="yellow">Every child was conceived with love.</font>

166
00:18:30,170 --> 00:18:31,340
<font color="yellow">Stop torturing them.</font>

167
00:18:31,340 --> 00:18:33,670
<font color="yellow">Get rid of the hands that are covering his eyes.</font>

168
00:18:33,710 --> 00:18:35,340
<font color="yellow">Let them recognize each other.</font>

169
00:18:35,340 --> 00:18:37,010
<font color="yellow">Let them make their own decision.</font>

170
00:18:37,910 --> 00:18:39,140
<font color="yellow">It's too bad.</font>

171
00:18:39,410 --> 00:18:41,040
<font color="yellow">I loved him for his good looks.</font>

172
00:18:52,940 --> 00:18:54,640
<font color="yellow">They are finally here.</font>

173
00:19:25,240 --> 00:19:26,340
<font color="yellow">Deok Hwa.</font>

174
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:49,810
<font color="yellow">Who are you?</font>

175
00:19:49,980 --> 00:19:51,510
<font color="yellow">Let's introduce each other.</font>

176
00:19:54,940 --> 00:19:57,640
<font color="yellow">Please, no...</font>

177
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:59,910
<font color="yellow">Please...</font>

178
00:19:59,910 --> 00:20:02,140
<font color="yellow">Don't pray to anyone. The almighty is not listening.</font>

179
00:20:02,140 --> 00:20:04,610
<font color="yellow">"The almighty is still not listening."</font>

180
00:20:05,410 --> 00:20:06,770
<font color="yellow">You were whining.</font>

181
00:20:08,410 --> 00:20:11,040
<font color="yellow">"The almighty must have had his reason for erasing my memory."</font>

182
00:20:11,270 --> 00:20:14,710
<font color="yellow">I will live whether or not I remember my memories.</font>

183
00:20:14,870 --> 00:20:16,240
<font color="yellow">The almighty must have his reasons.</font>

184
00:20:16,240 --> 00:20:17,670
<font color="yellow">You were guessing my intention.</font>

185
00:20:19,980 --> 00:20:21,640
<font color="yellow">I was always listening.</font>

186
00:20:21,910 --> 00:20:24,210
<font color="yellow">You were pleading for death, so I gave you a chance.</font>

187
00:20:24,270 --> 00:20:25,480
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

188
00:20:25,910 --> 00:20:27,840
<font color="yellow">why are you still alive?</font>

189
00:20:28,910 --> 00:20:30,270
<font color="yellow">I never erased your memory.</font>

190
00:20:30,270 --> 00:20:33,370
<font color="yellow">You chose to have your memory erased and yet,</font>

191
00:20:34,540 --> 00:20:38,240
<font color="yellow">you think it's the almighty's plan or mistake?</font>

192
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:42,640
<font color="yellow">The almighty simply questions.</font>

193
00:20:42,640 --> 00:20:44,640
<font color="yellow">Fate is the question I throw.</font>

194
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:45,640
<font color="yellow">You...</font>

195
00:20:48,270 --> 00:20:49,670
<font color="yellow">can find the answer.</font>

196
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:54,510
<font color="yellow">You can say bye...</font>

197
00:20:56,410 --> 00:20:57,540
<font color="yellow">to this boy too.</font>

198
00:20:58,270 --> 00:20:59,370
<font color="yellow">Well, then.</font>

199
00:21:00,170 --> 00:21:01,310
<font color="yellow">I'll get going then.</font>

200
00:21:39,940 --> 00:21:41,640
<font color="yellow">Why are you two here?</font>

201
00:21:42,610 --> 00:21:43,670
<font color="yellow">When did you come?</font>

202
00:21:44,710 --> 00:21:46,270
<font color="yellow">Why am I on the floor?</font>

203
00:21:52,070 --> 00:21:53,110
<font color="yellow">No way.</font>

204
00:21:53,840 --> 00:21:55,740
<font color="yellow">Did I just black out?</font>

205
00:21:57,070 --> 00:21:58,210
<font color="yellow">But I just had one drink.</font>

206
00:22:00,940 --> 00:22:02,340
<font color="yellow">Whoever you are,</font>

207
00:22:03,070 --> 00:22:04,370
<font color="yellow">let me hit you once.</font>

208
00:22:05,770 --> 00:22:07,010
<font color="yellow">Why would you hit him?</font>

209
00:22:07,510 --> 00:22:08,940
<font color="yellow">He doesn't have anything to do with it.</font>

210
00:22:08,940 --> 00:22:10,340
<font color="yellow">Are you siding with him?</font>

211
00:22:10,970 --> 00:22:13,870
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry I kept asking you to go somewhere with me.</font>

212
00:22:13,870 --> 00:22:14,910
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

213
00:22:15,610 --> 00:22:16,940
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with him?</font>

214
00:22:16,940 --> 00:22:18,640
<font color="yellow">Are you serious?</font>

215
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:20,740
<font color="yellow">Are you really Deok Hwa?</font>

216
00:22:20,970 --> 00:22:24,440
<font color="yellow">He's a butterfly. A butterfly.</font>

217
00:22:24,440 --> 00:22:25,540
<font color="yellow">You must be drunk.</font>

218
00:22:25,540 --> 00:22:27,010
<font color="yellow">Come here. Come here!</font>

219
00:22:27,010 --> 00:22:28,970
<font color="yellow">Let go of me. Let me talk to him.</font>

220
00:22:28,970 --> 00:22:30,440
<font color="yellow">Let go of me. Let go.</font>

221
00:22:34,410 --> 00:22:36,410
<font color="yellow">It's hot. It's hot.</font>

222
00:22:39,170 --> 00:22:41,040
<font color="yellow">It's really good.</font>

223
00:22:41,040 --> 00:22:42,640
<font color="yellow">It turns out he's a grim reaper.</font>

224
00:22:45,870 --> 00:22:48,740
<font color="yellow">How did you find out?</font>

225
00:22:48,940 --> 00:22:52,170
<font color="yellow">I witnessed a very strange moment.</font>

226
00:22:52,170 --> 00:22:53,910
<font color="yellow">We happened...</font>

227
00:22:54,610 --> 00:22:57,270
<font color="yellow">to cross paths a few times in my life.</font>

228
00:22:57,270 --> 00:22:59,210
<font color="yellow">Sorry I didn't tell you.</font>

229
00:22:59,210 --> 00:23:02,070
<font color="yellow">For a grim reaper, Woo Bin's...</font>

230
00:23:02,110 --> 00:23:04,270
<font color="yellow">really sweet, gentle, and...</font>

231
00:23:04,270 --> 00:23:07,270
<font color="yellow">Does he have a clingy ghost ex-girlfriend?</font>

232
00:23:08,510 --> 00:23:10,040
<font color="yellow">That was the first thought I had.</font>

233
00:23:10,040 --> 00:23:13,610
<font color="yellow">We aren't a good match. I'm way out of his league.</font>

234
00:23:13,610 --> 00:23:15,010
<font color="yellow">We live in two separate worlds.</font>

235
00:23:15,010 --> 00:23:17,770
<font color="yellow">How did you think of that?</font>

236
00:23:19,410 --> 00:23:21,040
<font color="yellow">I even had this thought.</font>

237
00:23:21,540 --> 00:23:25,210
<font color="yellow">If he's a grim reaper, then the man who says he's my brother...</font>

238
00:23:25,210 --> 00:23:27,910
<font color="yellow">must have really lived for nearly 1,000 years.</font>

239
00:23:29,270 --> 00:23:32,670
<font color="yellow">Is that true? Are you the wife of the goblin?</font>

240
00:23:32,670 --> 00:23:36,470
<font color="yellow">Technically speaking, I am his wife,</font>

241
00:23:36,540 --> 00:23:38,040
<font color="yellow">but I'm the breadwinner.</font>

242
00:23:38,540 --> 00:23:39,870
<font color="yellow">This is insane.</font>

243
00:23:41,710 --> 00:23:43,040
<font color="yellow">Boss.</font>

244
00:23:43,040 --> 00:23:45,470
<font color="yellow">Even if you hang out outside of our house,</font>

245
00:23:45,470 --> 00:23:48,170
<font color="yellow">it's very unlikely that you'll see Woo Bin.</font>

246
00:23:48,170 --> 00:23:50,340
<font color="yellow">He works late very often.</font>

247
00:23:50,340 --> 00:23:51,810
<font color="yellow">Give him a call.</font>

248
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:54,640
<font color="yellow">How can I when he suggested we break up?</font>

249
00:23:54,640 --> 00:23:58,410
<font color="yellow">I'd force myself to take his call if he were to contact me first.</font>

250
00:23:58,870 --> 00:24:00,110
<font color="yellow">Just play along.</font>

251
00:24:00,340 --> 00:24:01,340
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

252
00:24:02,510 --> 00:24:05,340
<font color="yellow">Boss, I'm really sorry but...</font>

253
00:24:05,540 --> 00:24:07,070
<font color="yellow">Sure, do what you want.</font>

254
00:24:07,140 --> 00:24:08,940
<font color="yellow">I didn't say anything yet.</font>

255
00:24:08,940 --> 00:24:11,670
<font color="yellow">You're in college now and you want to work different hours.</font>

256
00:24:11,870 --> 00:24:13,070
<font color="yellow">That's incredible.</font>

257
00:24:14,510 --> 00:24:18,470
<font color="yellow">You're a real human being, right?</font>

258
00:24:27,270 --> 00:24:28,470
<font color="yellow">Welcome.</font>

259
00:24:35,710 --> 00:24:39,770
<font color="yellow">It's been a while since I got startled by a human.</font>

260
00:24:40,410 --> 00:24:41,470
<font color="yellow">Me, too.</font>

261
00:24:42,010 --> 00:24:44,610
<font color="yellow">Why are we eating chicken anyway?</font>

262
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:47,040
<font color="yellow">The owner lives in the flat beneath mine.</font>

263
00:24:47,070 --> 00:24:49,070
<font color="yellow">We should help our neighbours.</font>

264
00:24:49,070 --> 00:24:51,140
<font color="yellow">Let's eat up and get going.</font>

265
00:24:51,340 --> 00:24:54,070
<font color="yellow">Early January is the busiest time of year.</font>

266
00:24:58,170 --> 00:24:59,470
<font color="yellow">Enjoy your meal.</font>

267
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:01,470
<font color="yellow">We didn't order this.</font>

268
00:25:01,510 --> 00:25:04,510
<font color="yellow">It's on the house. It's a new menu. You guys have a tough job.</font>

269
00:25:04,510 --> 00:25:07,170
<font color="yellow">Thanks so much for noticing.</font>

270
00:25:09,540 --> 00:25:11,640
<font color="yellow">It tastes delicious.</font>

271
00:25:13,140 --> 00:25:14,340
<font color="yellow">What's the matter?</font>

272
00:25:15,070 --> 00:25:17,170
<font color="yellow">- Eat up. - I'll dip it first.</font>

273
00:25:23,170 --> 00:25:27,170
<font color="yellow">How dare a ghost appear in front of a grim reaper?</font>

274
00:25:27,240 --> 00:25:28,810
<font color="yellow">It has been a while.</font>

275
00:25:29,910 --> 00:25:32,910
<font color="yellow">I see you have been living as a grim reaper.</font>

276
00:25:33,010 --> 00:25:36,070
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about? Do you know me?</font>

277
00:25:36,070 --> 00:25:38,870
<font color="yellow">- I do. - You can't trick me.</font>

278
00:25:38,870 --> 00:25:41,670
<font color="yellow">Do you not want to know who I am?</font>

279
00:25:41,770 --> 00:25:45,310
<font color="yellow">And why I am so fearless as I stand here before you?</font>

280
00:25:45,810 --> 00:25:47,370
<font color="yellow">But most importantly,</font>

281
00:25:50,040 --> 00:25:53,270
<font color="yellow">do you not want to know who you are?</font>

282
00:25:56,910 --> 00:25:59,740
<font color="yellow">Go and hold the woman's hand.</font>

283
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:03,270
<font color="yellow">I'm talking about the owner of the restaurant you just left.</font>

284
00:26:04,640 --> 00:26:08,710
<font color="yellow">People who committed serious crimes are born again as grim reapers.</font>

285
00:26:08,870 --> 00:26:11,840
<font color="yellow">She will show you what you did.</font>

286
00:26:11,910 --> 00:26:13,010
<font color="yellow">And also...</font>

287
00:26:13,870 --> 00:26:17,240
<font color="yellow">what part I played in it.</font>

288
00:26:25,210 --> 00:26:26,610
<font color="yellow">I never erased your memory.</font>

289
00:26:26,610 --> 00:26:29,710
<font color="yellow">You chose to have your memory erased and yet,</font>

290
00:26:30,510 --> 00:26:34,610
<font color="yellow">you think it's the almighty's plan or mistake?</font>

291
00:26:40,910 --> 00:26:42,870
<font color="yellow">What are you thinking about?</font>

292
00:26:44,010 --> 00:26:45,540
<font color="yellow">Something I shouldn't think about.</font>

293
00:26:45,910 --> 00:26:49,270
<font color="yellow">Why are you doing what you know you shouldn't?</font>

294
00:26:49,270 --> 00:26:52,410
<font color="yellow">If I don't do it today, I might do it tomorrow.</font>

295
00:26:53,310 --> 00:26:56,340
<font color="yellow">Don't do that. It's a bad time.</font>

296
00:26:57,240 --> 00:27:01,770
<font color="yellow">We got a warning from the top because of the Janghang-dong case.</font>

297
00:27:03,040 --> 00:27:04,170
<font color="yellow">What did they say?</font>

298
00:27:04,270 --> 00:27:07,670
<font color="yellow">"Remember that you are sinners."</font>

299
00:27:08,910 --> 00:27:11,040
<font color="yellow">It's so confusing and worrying.</font>

300
00:27:11,470 --> 00:27:13,470
<font color="yellow">Here are this month's name cards.</font>

301
00:27:14,810 --> 00:27:16,610
<font color="yellow">Was I given an answer...</font>

302
00:27:17,710 --> 00:27:19,470
<font color="yellow">or a question?</font>

303
00:27:19,670 --> 00:27:21,140
<font color="yellow">I gave you name cards.</font>

304
00:27:39,810 --> 00:27:41,540
<font color="yellow">I'm home.</font>

305
00:27:47,140 --> 00:27:48,470
<font color="yellow">He has three hours.</font>

306
00:27:48,970 --> 00:27:51,770
<font color="yellow">Cause of death is cardiac arrest.</font>

307
00:27:52,670 --> 00:27:54,170
<font color="yellow">You should say goodbye.</font>

308
00:27:54,540 --> 00:27:56,840
<font color="yellow">I said all I wanted to during our lifetime.</font>

309
00:27:58,540 --> 00:28:00,040
<font color="yellow">I don't want to see him...</font>

310
00:28:01,010 --> 00:28:03,540
<font color="yellow">feel sorry for me or be apologetic.</font>

311
00:28:06,270 --> 00:28:09,040
<font color="yellow">See him off for me.</font>

312
00:28:10,070 --> 00:28:11,370
<font color="yellow">I will.</font>

313
00:28:11,940 --> 00:28:13,710
<font color="yellow">Tell him to be born again.</font>

314
00:28:15,370 --> 00:28:16,840
<font color="yellow">In his next life,</font>

315
00:28:18,910 --> 00:28:21,840
<font color="yellow">tell him not to serve any man and to be free.</font>

316
00:28:23,610 --> 00:28:25,070
<font color="yellow">Tell him I thank him.</font>

317
00:28:27,470 --> 00:28:29,470
<font color="yellow">That I was very grateful.</font>

318
00:28:47,940 --> 00:28:50,040
<font color="yellow">What is going on?</font>

319
00:28:50,210 --> 00:28:54,170
<font color="yellow">Prepare a black outfit. You'll hear of Chairman Yu's death.</font>

320
00:28:55,970 --> 00:28:58,540
<font color="yellow">Check on him every now and then.</font>

321
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:07,670
<font color="yellow">You're so mean, you don't know how I feel</font>

322
00:30:08,040 --> 00:30:11,110
<font color="yellow">This is unbearable. My back hurts.</font>

323
00:30:13,540 --> 00:30:15,110
<font color="yellow">Just wait until I'm CEO.</font>

324
00:30:15,810 --> 00:30:18,540
<font color="yellow">I'll come here every day, drag everyone out to dinner,</font>

325
00:30:18,540 --> 00:30:20,540
<font color="yellow">and check their work.</font>

326
00:30:21,410 --> 00:30:24,540
<font color="yellow">I'll compliment your worst outfit and make you wear it forever.</font>

327
00:30:27,870 --> 00:30:29,910
<font color="yellow">- Deok Hwa. - What?</font>

328
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:32,670
<font color="yellow">Did Grandpa tell you to watch me from up close?</font>

329
00:30:32,770 --> 00:30:34,670
<font color="yellow">You need to come with me. Right now.</font>

330
00:30:34,670 --> 00:30:36,440
<font color="yellow">I don't get off work for hours.</font>

331
00:30:36,440 --> 00:30:39,010
<font color="yellow">I brought your suit. Change in the car.</font>

332
00:30:41,170 --> 00:30:42,540
<font color="yellow">What suit?</font>

333
00:31:38,340 --> 00:31:41,270
<font color="yellow">The man whose every second on this earth was good...</font>

334
00:31:42,270 --> 00:31:43,840
<font color="yellow">Here he rests.</font>

335
00:31:44,470 --> 00:31:45,670
<font color="yellow">Yu Shin Woo.</font>

336
00:31:50,740 --> 00:31:54,740
<font color="yellow">(The man whose every second on this earth was good.)</font>

337
00:31:54,840 --> 00:32:00,110
<font color="yellow">(Here he rests. Yu Shin Woo.)</font>

338
00:32:31,690 --> 00:32:33,320
<font color="yellow">So this is what it's like...</font>

339
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:36,460
<font color="yellow">to be immortal.</font>

340
00:32:41,290 --> 00:32:45,420
<font color="yellow">Chairman Yu must keep turning back to look.</font>

341
00:32:48,720 --> 00:32:51,760
<font color="yellow">He'd be worried about you.</font>

342
00:32:54,620 --> 00:32:56,060
<font color="yellow">That's why...</font>

343
00:32:57,260 --> 00:32:58,720
<font color="yellow">the ones left behind...</font>

344
00:32:59,220 --> 00:33:01,290
<font color="yellow">should live even harder.</font>

345
00:33:02,760 --> 00:33:04,860
<font color="yellow">We might cry from time to time,</font>

346
00:33:06,190 --> 00:33:07,820
<font color="yellow">but we should smile a lot...</font>

347
00:33:09,230 --> 00:33:10,890
<font color="yellow">and cheer up.</font>

348
00:33:13,520 --> 00:33:14,730
<font color="yellow">You're...</font>

349
00:33:16,120 --> 00:33:19,490
<font color="yellow">obligated to do that in return for the love you received.</font>

350
00:33:26,760 --> 00:33:27,990
<font color="yellow">Would you like...</font>

351
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:30,620
<font color="yellow">something to warm you up?</font>

352
00:33:38,020 --> 00:33:39,160
<font color="yellow">I'll have something...</font>

353
00:33:40,990 --> 00:33:43,060
<font color="yellow">with Deok Hwa when he's back.</font>

354
00:34:00,090 --> 00:34:01,490
<font color="yellow">What do I do now?</font>

355
00:34:04,260 --> 00:34:06,190
<font color="yellow">I didn't get to treat him well.</font>

356
00:34:06,960 --> 00:34:08,390
<font color="yellow">How can he leave me...</font>

357
00:34:09,460 --> 00:34:12,860
<font color="yellow">making me feeling guilty like this?</font>

358
00:34:14,990 --> 00:34:18,290
<font color="yellow">How can I keep living while feeling sorry to him?</font>

359
00:34:24,120 --> 00:34:26,160
<font color="yellow">What do I do now?</font>

360
00:34:27,790 --> 00:34:30,690
<font color="yellow">How will I live alone?</font>

361
00:34:34,190 --> 00:34:35,960
<font color="yellow">You're not alone.</font>

362
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:40,760
<font color="yellow">Uncle.</font>

363
00:34:41,290 --> 00:34:42,990
<font color="yellow">You have me.</font>

364
00:34:43,090 --> 00:34:44,790
<font color="yellow">You and I will be together,</font>

365
00:34:44,890 --> 00:34:46,860
<font color="yellow">so don't worry.</font>

366
00:34:47,860 --> 00:34:49,490
<font color="yellow">Uncle...</font>

367
00:35:03,860 --> 00:35:05,560
<font color="yellow">You should get up and eat something.</font>

368
00:35:07,890 --> 00:35:09,790
<font color="yellow">Come on, these apples look like rabbits.</font>

369
00:35:12,820 --> 00:35:14,590
<font color="yellow">Do you want me to make you gold?</font>

370
00:35:17,760 --> 00:35:19,590
<font color="yellow">Do you want me to walk through walls?</font>

371
00:35:20,890 --> 00:35:24,090
<font color="yellow">Deok Hwa, you can have my camera.</font>

372
00:35:24,090 --> 00:35:26,090
<font color="yellow">I know you wanted it.</font>

373
00:35:28,190 --> 00:35:32,120
<font color="yellow">Forget it. My grandpa got it for you.</font>

374
00:35:34,660 --> 00:35:36,520
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry I couldn't tell you in advance.</font>

375
00:35:37,590 --> 00:35:41,060
<font color="yellow">I should have given you time to get yourself together.</font>

376
00:35:41,290 --> 00:35:42,390
<font color="yellow">I regret it.</font>

377
00:35:43,660 --> 00:35:46,590
<font color="yellow">However, there's order in this world.</font>

378
00:35:46,590 --> 00:35:47,690
<font color="yellow">I know.</font>

379
00:35:47,790 --> 00:35:50,390
<font color="yellow">We've been tending a goblin for generations.</font>

380
00:35:57,860 --> 00:35:59,490
<font color="yellow">Thank you, everyone.</font>

381
00:36:00,290 --> 00:36:02,090
<font color="yellow">I have to go do something.</font>

382
00:36:16,460 --> 00:36:18,960
<font color="yellow">I thought he might be bothered by this.</font>

383
00:36:20,190 --> 00:36:22,230
<font color="yellow">You know what he's like.</font>

384
00:36:23,090 --> 00:36:24,190
<font color="yellow">I do.</font>

385
00:36:24,690 --> 00:36:27,320
<font color="yellow">Mr. Kim has been appointed as the CEO.</font>

386
00:36:27,890 --> 00:36:30,190
<font color="yellow">Grandpa had everything prepared before he left.</font>

387
00:36:31,790 --> 00:36:33,190
<font color="yellow">I'm glad.</font>

388
00:36:33,730 --> 00:36:35,890
<font color="yellow">I'm not ready yet.</font>

389
00:36:39,560 --> 00:36:40,620
<font color="yellow">Right.</font>

390
00:36:45,190 --> 00:36:47,160
<font color="yellow">I'll start learning the work from the ground up.</font>

391
00:36:47,820 --> 00:36:50,360
<font color="yellow">I bet that's what he would have wanted.</font>

392
00:36:52,020 --> 00:36:54,320
<font color="yellow">- Okay. - I'll also...</font>

393
00:36:57,760 --> 00:36:58,890
<font color="yellow">start learning go.</font>

394
00:36:59,860 --> 00:37:03,090
<font color="yellow">Then I'll become your brother, your father,</font>

395
00:37:03,490 --> 00:37:05,360
<font color="yellow">then your grandfather.</font>

396
00:37:07,820 --> 00:37:09,060
<font color="yellow">Just like my grandfather.</font>

397
00:37:13,320 --> 00:37:14,490
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

398
00:37:24,190 --> 00:37:26,120
<font color="yellow">(Yu Deok Hwa)</font>

399
00:37:39,590 --> 00:37:41,120
<font color="yellow">(Kim Do Young)</font>

400
00:37:47,390 --> 00:37:49,020
<font color="yellow">If someone...</font>

401
00:37:49,020 --> 00:37:53,520
<font color="yellow">by the last name Kim and first name Shin comes to you...</font>

402
00:37:53,520 --> 00:37:56,960
<font color="yellow">and says that he is here to retrieve his belongings,</font>

403
00:37:56,960 --> 00:37:58,090
<font color="yellow">give it to him.</font>

404
00:37:58,460 --> 00:38:02,460
<font color="yellow">All I've left behind belongs to him.</font>

405
00:38:02,860 --> 00:38:05,390
<font color="yellow">He will come to you through rain...</font>

406
00:38:05,390 --> 00:38:08,090
<font color="yellow">and leave as a blue flame.</font>

407
00:38:08,360 --> 00:38:11,260
<font color="yellow">Then you will know it's him.</font>

408
00:38:31,060 --> 00:38:32,160
<font color="yellow">He left, right?</font>

409
00:38:36,420 --> 00:38:38,760
<font color="yellow">Who are... Do you know me?</font>

410
00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:41,790
<font color="yellow">I do. A kid who is nothing but nice.</font>

411
00:38:42,090 --> 00:38:44,520
<font color="yellow">That's why you light up this world.</font>

412
00:38:45,120 --> 00:38:48,590
<font color="yellow">Remember, your good-nature is what will bring you luck.</font>

413
00:38:49,020 --> 00:38:50,260
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

414
00:38:50,460 --> 00:38:52,760
<font color="yellow">I'm not a kid, though.</font>

415
00:38:53,420 --> 00:38:54,890
<font color="yellow">Do you want to go for a drink?</font>

416
00:38:54,890 --> 00:38:57,360
<font color="yellow">You can go drinking with someone beautiful.</font>

417
00:38:57,360 --> 00:38:58,490
<font color="yellow">You are beautiful.</font>

418
00:38:58,490 --> 00:39:00,360
<font color="yellow">You should drink with a human.</font>

419
00:39:01,460 --> 00:39:02,490
<font color="yellow">Bye.</font>

420
00:39:07,120 --> 00:39:08,260
<font color="yellow">What was that?</font>

421
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:14,190
<font color="yellow">Why are you making so much?</font>

422
00:39:14,190 --> 00:39:15,460
<font color="yellow">Deok Hwa is coming.</font>

423
00:39:18,230 --> 00:39:19,360
<font color="yellow">Pass me the pepper.</font>

424
00:39:21,020 --> 00:39:23,790
<font color="yellow">I'm jealous of Deok Hwa. He has an uncle.</font>

425
00:39:24,890 --> 00:39:26,390
<font color="yellow">Don't mind me.</font>

426
00:39:26,390 --> 00:39:29,860
<font color="yellow">I'm jealous of everyone and I feel empty these days.</font>

427
00:39:29,860 --> 00:39:31,120
<font color="yellow">Just tell me right out.</font>

428
00:39:31,120 --> 00:39:32,520
<font color="yellow">I know you want an uncle like me.</font>

429
00:39:32,520 --> 00:39:34,760
<font color="yellow">A super handsome uncle.</font>

430
00:39:42,690 --> 00:39:43,730
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

