00:56:39,510 --> 00:56:41,310
<font color="yellow">his sister's history.</font>

647
00:56:43,110 --> 00:56:46,880
<font color="yellow">There are three people who committed great sins in history around then.</font>

648
00:56:48,010 --> 00:56:50,950
<font color="yellow">Kim Shin, who cut off the heads of the enemies.</font>

649
00:56:52,480 --> 00:56:56,880
<font color="yellow">Wang Yeo, who ordered the death of Kim Shin...</font>

650
00:56:57,380 --> 00:56:58,480
<font color="yellow">and his sister.</font>

651
00:57:00,580 --> 00:57:02,510
<font color="yellow">And the one who led...</font>

652
00:57:02,880 --> 00:57:06,110
<font color="yellow">Kim Shin and his sister to their grave...</font>

653
00:57:07,050 --> 00:57:08,280
<font color="yellow">Park Joong Won.</font>

654
00:57:08,710 --> 00:57:12,650
<font color="yellow">Kim Shin is still alive.</font>

655
00:57:13,450 --> 00:57:16,750
<font color="yellow">and Kim Sun was reincarnated as Sunny.</font>

656
00:57:18,110 --> 00:57:21,710
<font color="yellow">That means I am Wang Yeo...</font>

657
00:57:23,450 --> 00:57:25,810
<font color="yellow">or Park Joong Won.</font>

658
00:57:26,880 --> 00:57:28,780
<font color="yellow">That's is all I've thought about.</font>

659
00:57:29,880 --> 00:57:32,310
<font color="yellow">The nameless grim reaper.</font>

660
00:57:32,550 --> 00:57:35,480
<font color="yellow">He is Wang Yeo.</font>

661
00:57:37,210 --> 00:57:38,410
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

662
00:57:39,880 --> 00:57:41,950
<font color="yellow">regardless of which one I am,</font>

663
00:57:44,050 --> 00:57:47,580
<font color="yellow">I am Shin's enemy, aren't I?</font>

664
00:57:50,250 --> 00:57:53,050
<font color="yellow">Regardless of which one I am,</font>

665
00:57:56,410 --> 00:57:58,010
<font color="yellow">Sunny and I...</font>

666
00:57:59,550 --> 00:58:01,180
<font color="yellow">cannot be, right?</font>

667
00:58:20,780 --> 00:58:24,450
<font color="yellow">Oh my gosh. I almost hit you.</font>

668
00:58:24,810 --> 00:58:27,310
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry. Did I startle you?</font>

669
00:58:27,580 --> 00:58:29,950
<font color="yellow">Yes, a little.</font>

670
00:58:30,150 --> 00:58:32,150
<font color="yellow">Sorry, but we're closed.</font>

671
00:58:32,310 --> 00:58:34,680
<font color="yellow">You're right. Okay then.</font>

672
00:58:35,410 --> 00:58:36,680
<font color="yellow">See you later.</font>

673
00:58:44,310 --> 00:58:46,510
<font color="yellow">Okay. Come back another time.</font>

674
00:58:52,750 --> 00:58:54,110
<font color="yellow">No. Never.</font>

675
00:58:55,080 --> 00:58:57,650
<font color="yellow">Do not serve her any medicine.</font>

676
00:58:59,650 --> 00:59:01,480
<font color="yellow">Your Majesty reigns over his people,</font>

677
00:59:01,480 --> 00:59:03,310
<font color="yellow">and it's said Your Majesty is controlled by a divinity.</font>

678
00:59:03,350 --> 00:59:06,510
<font color="yellow">Apparently, this divinity refers to Kim Shin.</font>

679
00:59:22,480 --> 00:59:24,180
<font color="yellow">(Kim Woo Bin)</font>

680
00:59:31,880 --> 00:59:33,050
<font color="yellow">Hello?</font>

681
00:59:33,350 --> 00:59:36,050
<font color="yellow">Let's meet.</font>

682
00:59:36,810 --> 00:59:38,550
<font color="yellow">You wanted to break up.</font>

683
00:59:39,410 --> 00:59:41,880
<font color="yellow">I'm in front of your home.</font>

684
00:59:42,750 --> 00:59:45,480
<font color="yellow">Wait right there. Is he insane?</font>

685
01:00:06,980 --> 01:00:09,010
<font color="yellow">How could you just show up like this?</font>

686
01:00:09,750 --> 01:00:11,710
<font color="yellow">I was home, so I have no makeup on.</font>

687
01:00:15,480 --> 01:00:17,810
<font color="yellow">I came to get my ring back.</font>

688
01:00:17,950 --> 01:00:20,150
<font color="yellow">We still have that excuse left.</font>

689
01:00:25,950 --> 01:00:28,350
<font color="yellow">Why do you look like that?</font>

690
01:00:29,410 --> 01:00:31,210
<font color="yellow">Didn't you come because you missed me?</font>

691
01:00:33,650 --> 01:00:34,850
<font color="yellow">I did.</font>

692
01:00:35,050 --> 01:00:36,950
<font color="yellow">- But? - But...</font>

693
01:00:37,580 --> 01:00:39,680
<font color="yellow">I am afraid I may be...</font>

694
01:00:41,580 --> 01:00:43,210
<font color="yellow">a certain somebody.</font>

695
01:00:45,750 --> 01:00:47,380
<font color="yellow">I take a step back.</font>

696
01:00:48,810 --> 01:00:50,480
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

697
01:00:50,980 --> 01:00:53,050
<font color="yellow">Everything about me is wrong.</font>

698
01:00:56,880 --> 01:00:59,350
<font color="yellow">I sincerely hope that this choice...</font>

699
01:01:00,250 --> 01:01:01,410
<font color="yellow">is the right one.</font>

700
01:01:03,480 --> 01:01:06,150
<font color="yellow">- Don't do this. - As I am not alive,</font>

701
01:01:08,110 --> 01:01:09,680
<font color="yellow">I have no name.</font>

702
01:01:10,750 --> 01:01:12,010
<font color="yellow">You...</font>

703
01:01:13,650 --> 01:01:14,780
<font color="yellow">asked after me.</font>

704
01:01:18,550 --> 01:01:20,380
<font color="yellow">Thank you for that.</font>

705
01:01:22,150 --> 01:01:23,380
<font color="yellow">I said stop.</font>

706
01:01:23,380 --> 01:01:25,210
<font color="yellow">The kiss of a grim reaper...</font>

707
01:01:27,210 --> 01:01:29,280
<font color="yellow">brings back memories of your previous life.</font>

708
01:01:31,480 --> 01:01:33,180
<font color="yellow">I fear what I was...</font>

709
01:01:34,310 --> 01:01:37,150
<font color="yellow">in your previous life.</font>

710
01:01:37,880 --> 01:01:41,480
<font color="yellow">But I wish you are left only with good memories.</font>

711
01:01:43,810 --> 01:01:45,050
<font color="yellow">I hope that...</font>

712
01:01:46,550 --> 01:01:48,980
<font color="yellow">a part of them are memories...</font>

713
01:01:50,310 --> 01:01:51,580
<font color="yellow">of your older brother.</font>

714
01:01:52,210 --> 01:01:53,280
<font color="yellow">And...</font>

715
01:01:54,550 --> 01:01:56,450
<font color="yellow">I hope that he is...</font>

716
01:01:58,180 --> 01:01:59,610
<font color="yellow">Kim Shin.</font>

717
01:02:41,850 --> 01:02:44,150
<font color="yellow">Your brother has returned in triumph again.</font>

718
01:02:44,850 --> 01:02:46,480
<font color="yellow">Between the two of us,</font>

719
01:02:46,580 --> 01:02:48,550
<font color="yellow">whom do you wish to be alive?</font>

720
01:02:49,880 --> 01:02:51,750
<font color="yellow">- Your Majesty. - Answer me.</font>

721
01:02:52,810 --> 01:02:55,880
<font color="yellow">Or have you already made your decision?</font>

722
01:02:56,550 --> 01:03:00,180
<font color="yellow">Of course, whether I live or your brother lives,</font>

723
01:03:02,410 --> 01:03:04,050
<font color="yellow">you have nothing to lose.</font>

724
01:03:05,550 --> 01:03:07,250
<font color="yellow">You're a fool, Your Majesty.</font>

725
01:03:08,150 --> 01:03:10,010
<font color="yellow">Do you want to die?</font>

726
01:03:11,450 --> 01:03:13,180
<font color="yellow">Why are you dressed like that?</font>

727
01:03:15,580 --> 01:03:19,080
<font color="yellow">You are already mourning.</font>

728
01:03:20,250 --> 01:03:22,380
<font color="yellow">Bring the queen's jewellery box.</font>

729
01:03:29,380 --> 01:03:31,150
<font color="yellow">Why aren't you wearing anything?</font>

730
01:03:31,150 --> 01:03:33,850
<font color="yellow">I did not give you these to keep in a box!</font>

731
01:03:36,550 --> 01:03:38,450
<font color="yellow">I can't tell anymore.</font>

732
01:03:39,180 --> 01:03:41,510
<font color="yellow">I don't know if my enemies are the barbarians or your brother.</font>

733
01:03:41,510 --> 01:03:43,380
<font color="yellow">Park Joong Won is your enemy.</font>

734
01:04:02,480 --> 01:04:04,980
<font color="yellow">Your brother, the man that the barbarians could not kill...</font>

735
01:04:05,950 --> 01:04:07,250
<font color="yellow">I will kill him today.</font>

736
01:04:07,250 --> 01:04:08,350
<font color="yellow">Your Majesty.</font>

737
01:04:08,880 --> 01:04:10,450
<font color="yellow">Your brother's crime...</font>

738
01:04:11,550 --> 01:04:12,810
<font color="yellow">will be treason.</font>

739
01:04:15,880 --> 01:04:17,880
<font color="yellow">Wear this ring and greet him...</font>

740
01:04:17,980 --> 01:04:19,980
<font color="yellow">as my queen.</font>

741
01:04:42,050 --> 01:04:43,950
<font color="yellow">Whose side are you on?</font>

742
01:04:45,510 --> 01:04:48,380
<font color="yellow">Even once, were you ever on my side?</font>

743
01:04:48,950 --> 01:04:50,480
<font color="yellow">Even once,</font>

744
01:04:50,480 --> 01:04:52,550
<font color="yellow">did you ever care for me?</font>

745
01:04:52,750 --> 01:04:55,050
<font color="yellow">For one second, did you ever...</font>

746
01:04:58,210 --> 01:04:59,350
<font color="yellow">love me?</font>

747
01:05:10,810 --> 01:05:12,650
<font color="yellow">Do not side with him.</font>

748
01:05:15,180 --> 01:05:16,250
<font color="yellow">That is...</font>

749
01:05:17,610 --> 01:05:20,210
<font color="yellow">the only way you can preserve your life.</font>

750
01:05:23,980 --> 01:05:25,880
<font color="yellow">You have to make a choice.</font>

751
01:05:27,880 --> 01:05:30,110
<font color="yellow">Will you live as my woman...</font>

752
01:05:30,780 --> 01:05:32,550
<font color="yellow">or will you die...</font>

753
01:05:36,880 --> 01:05:38,410
<font color="yellow">as the traitor's sister?</font>

754
01:05:40,610 --> 01:05:42,880
<font color="yellow">The woman who loves you...</font>

755
01:05:46,250 --> 01:05:48,980
<font color="yellow">is the traitor's sister.</font>

756
01:06:31,410 --> 01:06:33,080
<font color="yellow">What was that?</font>

757
01:06:36,250 --> 01:06:37,850
<font color="yellow">What did I see?</font>

758
01:06:40,210 --> 01:06:41,520
<font color="yellow">What was that?</font>

759
01:06:42,580 --> 01:06:43,780
<font color="yellow">That was...</font>

760
01:06:44,650 --> 01:06:46,250
<font color="yellow">your past life.</font>

761
01:06:49,580 --> 01:06:50,750
<font color="yellow">Was...</font>

762
01:06:51,880 --> 01:06:53,810
<font color="yellow">Kim Shin...</font>

763
01:06:55,180 --> 01:06:56,880
<font color="yellow">in your past life?</font>

764
01:07:04,310 --> 01:07:05,480
<font color="yellow">Was I...</font>

765
01:07:07,410 --> 01:07:09,480
<font color="yellow">a part...</font>

766
01:07:13,580 --> 01:07:15,050
<font color="yellow">of your past life?</font>

767
01:07:35,210 --> 01:07:36,280
<font color="yellow">Can you...</font>

768
01:07:39,410 --> 01:07:41,880
<font color="yellow">look into my eyes?</font>

769
01:07:47,050 --> 01:07:50,580
<font color="yellow">Leave only the shining, happy memories...</font>

770
01:07:54,650 --> 01:07:56,020
<font color="yellow">and forget...</font>

771
01:07:57,810 --> 01:08:01,110
<font color="yellow">all the sad and hard moments.</font>

772
01:08:03,380 --> 01:08:06,810
<font color="yellow">Whether they were in your past life or present...</font>

773
01:08:09,210 --> 01:08:10,450
<font color="yellow">And...</font>

774
01:08:16,180 --> 01:08:17,650
<font color="yellow">forget about me.</font>

775
01:08:38,520 --> 01:08:39,880
<font color="yellow">I hope that...</font>

776
01:08:43,880 --> 01:08:46,450
<font color="yellow">you at least have a happy ending.</font>

777
01:09:56,980 --> 01:09:58,480
<font color="yellow">You, over there.</font>

778
01:09:59,020 --> 01:10:02,650
<font color="yellow">Why are you staring into my shop again?</font>

779
01:10:03,150 --> 01:10:04,580
<font color="yellow">What is it today?</font>

780
01:10:04,680 --> 01:10:08,020
<font color="yellow">An accessory? A biscuit? Socks?</font>

781
01:10:13,750 --> 01:10:15,380
<font color="yellow">I'm not here for that.</font>

782
01:10:17,150 --> 01:10:19,150
<font color="yellow">I owe you for the sweet potatoes.</font>

783
01:10:22,210 --> 01:10:24,310
<font color="yellow">Let's say that was my treat.</font>

784
01:10:33,880 --> 01:10:35,350
<font color="yellow">So, dear brother.</font>

785
01:10:37,880 --> 01:10:39,550
<font color="yellow">Did the king really say...</font>

786
01:10:40,310 --> 01:10:42,080
<font color="yellow">I was ugly?</font>

787
01:10:56,020 --> 01:10:58,750
<font color="yellow">Even if you're on the battlefield,</font>

788
01:11:00,250 --> 01:11:02,610
<font color="yellow">how can a brother not send his sister a reply?</font>

789
01:11:06,610 --> 01:11:07,710
<font color="yellow">Are you...</font>

790
01:11:10,520 --> 01:11:12,020
<font color="yellow">Are you really...</font>

791
01:11:12,550 --> 01:11:15,050
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry it took me this long to recognize you.</font>

792
01:11:16,380 --> 01:11:18,480
<font color="yellow">I promised to become happy,</font>

793
01:11:20,150 --> 01:11:21,750
<font color="yellow">but I couldn't keep it.</font>

794
01:11:26,580 --> 01:11:28,450
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

795
01:11:49,950 --> 01:11:52,780
<font color="yellow">Persimmon, flowery shoes, and silk.</font>

796
01:11:53,210 --> 01:11:54,810
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

797
01:12:14,880 --> 01:12:18,750
<font color="yellow">You must come see me more often from now on.</font>

798
01:12:43,580 --> 01:12:46,350
<font color="yellow">Can you help me if you're not too busy?</font>

799
01:13:04,350 --> 01:13:05,650
<font color="yellow">Is something wrong?</font>

800
01:13:05,950 --> 01:13:07,050
<font color="yellow">Just...</font>

801
01:13:08,050 --> 01:13:09,610
<font color="yellow">Something is bothering me.</font>

802
01:13:09,610 --> 01:13:11,310
<font color="yellow">Did you fight with my uncle again?</font>

803
01:13:11,350 --> 01:13:12,350
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

804
01:13:13,780 --> 01:13:15,080
<font color="yellow">Even before that.</font>

805
01:13:15,750 --> 01:13:18,310
<font color="yellow">Ever since that day, it's been happening.</font>

806
01:13:18,850 --> 01:13:19,880
<font color="yellow">When?</font>

807
01:13:32,250 --> 01:13:34,110
<font color="yellow">What is it? Are you okay?</font>

808
01:13:49,450 --> 01:13:51,580
<font color="yellow">That day?</font>

809
01:13:51,850 --> 01:13:53,480
<font color="yellow">It couldn't be because of him.</font>

810
01:13:53,550 --> 01:13:55,150
<font color="yellow">We were at a temple then.</font>

811
01:13:55,150 --> 01:13:56,610
<font color="yellow">- A temple? - Yes.</font>

812
01:13:56,750 --> 01:13:58,410
<font color="yellow">He sent up a lantern.</font>

813
01:13:58,410 --> 01:14:00,550
<font color="yellow">He does it once a year.</font>

814
01:14:01,650 --> 01:14:05,480
<font color="yellow">He does it in remembrance of the people he owes.</font>

815
01:14:05,680 --> 01:14:07,980
<font color="yellow">They had two syllable names.</font>

816
01:14:08,480 --> 01:14:10,650
<font color="yellow">Kim Sun...</font>

817
01:14:11,050 --> 01:14:13,480
<font color="yellow">and Wang something.</font>

818
01:14:13,480 --> 01:14:14,810
<font color="yellow">It was in Chinese characters.</font>

819
01:14:18,110 --> 01:14:19,950
<font color="yellow">What happens if I do this?</font>

820
01:14:25,210 --> 01:14:26,410
<font color="yellow">A pursued stone.</font>

821
01:14:29,750 --> 01:14:30,850
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

822
01:14:32,050 --> 01:14:33,110
<font color="yellow">Look at that.</font>

823
01:14:33,550 --> 01:14:35,020
<font color="yellow">She's acting like she can't see me.</font>

824
01:14:40,950 --> 01:14:44,110
<font color="yellow">Hey, you little punk!</font>

825
01:14:55,680 --> 01:14:57,710
<font color="yellow">She's not acting.</font>

826
01:14:58,880 --> 01:15:00,950
<font color="yellow">She really can't see me.</font>

827
01:15:13,210 --> 01:15:14,210
<font color="yellow">Me too.</font>

828
01:15:17,650 --> 01:15:18,650
<font color="yellow">Pardon?</font>

829
01:15:21,110 --> 01:15:24,250
<font color="yellow">I'm excited to pick you up, too.</font>

830
01:15:29,950 --> 01:15:34,310
<font color="yellow">I'm so happy you came to pick me up at school.</font>

831
01:15:35,680 --> 01:15:36,850
<font color="yellow">Forget it.</font>

832
01:15:38,750 --> 01:15:40,880
<font color="yellow">I was just thinking about something.</font>

833
01:15:41,450 --> 01:15:43,050
<font color="yellow">Did something good happen?</font>

834
01:15:43,050 --> 01:15:44,450
<font color="yellow">You look like it.</font>

835
01:15:44,450 --> 01:15:46,050
<font color="yellow">That took you a while to ask.</font>

836
01:15:47,150 --> 01:15:49,550
<font color="yellow">My sister, Sun...</font>

837
01:15:50,150 --> 01:15:51,350
<font color="yellow">finally remembered me.</font>

838
01:15:51,350 --> 01:15:53,480
<font color="yellow">Really? Really?</font>

839
01:15:53,480 --> 01:15:55,210
<font color="yellow">That's great news.</font>

840
01:15:55,350 --> 01:15:56,850
<font color="yellow">How?</font>

841
01:15:58,520 --> 01:16:00,210
<font color="yellow">I didn't ask her.</font>

842
01:16:00,650 --> 01:16:01,810
<font color="yellow">You're right.</font>

843
01:16:02,050 --> 01:16:03,850
<font color="yellow">How did she remember her previous life?</font>

844
01:16:06,150 --> 01:16:07,350
<font color="yellow">What's wrong?</font>

845
01:16:08,650 --> 01:16:10,050
<font color="yellow">Are you saying...</font>

846
01:16:12,650 --> 01:16:13,850
<font color="yellow">Can you...</font>

847
01:16:14,380 --> 01:16:16,850
<font color="yellow">pull the car over for a minute?</font>

848
01:16:24,380 --> 01:16:25,850
<font color="yellow">Please listen to me...</font>

849
01:16:26,550 --> 01:16:28,480
<font color="yellow">without getting upset.</font>

850
01:16:28,650 --> 01:16:31,020
<font color="yellow">I've thought about it a lot.</font>

851
01:16:32,580 --> 01:16:33,580
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

852
01:16:33,580 --> 01:16:37,410
<font color="yellow">I believe that you are someone much bigger...</font>

853
01:16:37,750 --> 01:16:39,380
<font color="yellow">than what I know.</font>

854
01:16:39,380 --> 01:16:40,810
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

855
01:16:43,110 --> 01:16:44,250
<font color="yellow">I...</font>

856
01:16:45,480 --> 01:16:47,980
<font color="yellow">met someone deceased,</font>

857
01:16:48,650 --> 01:16:49,850
<font color="yellow">and I think...</font>

858
01:16:50,680 --> 01:16:52,980
<font color="yellow">it's Park Joong Won.</font>

859
01:16:53,750 --> 01:16:54,750
<font color="yellow">How...</font>

860
01:16:56,050 --> 01:16:57,580
<font color="yellow">do you know Park Joong Won?</font>

861
01:16:57,580 --> 01:16:58,880
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry,</font>

862
01:16:59,680 --> 01:17:02,250
<font color="yellow">but overheard what you said...</font>

863
01:17:02,610 --> 01:17:04,150
<font color="yellow">to the Grim Reaper.</font>

864
01:17:04,250 --> 01:17:07,080
<font color="yellow">At first, I thought he was just an evil ghost.</font>

865
01:17:08,780 --> 01:17:11,580
<font color="yellow">However, I can't tell what he's after.</font>

866
01:17:11,880 --> 01:17:15,150
<font color="yellow">I feel like strange things happening around me are related to him.</font>

867
01:17:15,150 --> 01:17:17,780
<font color="yellow">Maybe Sunny remembering you...</font>

868
01:17:17,850 --> 01:17:19,750
<font color="yellow">might be because of him.</font>

869
01:17:19,750 --> 01:17:21,680
<font color="yellow">I'm glad you told me. Thank you.</font>

870
01:17:22,110 --> 01:17:24,850
<font color="yellow">I'll drive you home. Stay there and don't go out.</font>

871
01:17:25,310 --> 01:17:27,080
<font color="yellow">A goblin's house is the safest place.</font>

872
01:17:28,150 --> 01:17:29,150
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

873
01:18:42,150 --> 01:18:46,280
<font color="yellow">I avoided you for 900 years. I can't believe I ran into you.</font>

874
01:18:47,250 --> 01:18:48,780
<font color="yellow">How futile.</font>

875
01:18:51,020 --> 01:18:52,480
<font color="yellow">Do not worry.</font>

876
01:18:53,680 --> 01:18:55,580
<font color="yellow">I will get rid of you right away.</font>

877
01:18:56,210 --> 01:18:57,210
<font color="yellow">However,</font>

878
01:18:58,850 --> 01:19:00,950
<font color="yellow">you must tell me why you suddenly showed up...</font>

879
01:19:01,780 --> 01:19:04,550
<font color="yellow">after hiding for the last 900 years.</font>

880
01:19:05,350 --> 01:19:08,580
<font color="yellow">Despite all those years,</font>

881
01:19:08,580 --> 01:19:12,210
<font color="yellow">you have failed to find insight since you are a mere warrior.</font>

882
01:19:12,610 --> 01:19:17,380
<font color="yellow">You had your enemy trudge along with you. How pathetic.</font>

883
01:19:17,880 --> 01:19:20,650
<font color="yellow">I will be glad to tell you.</font>

884
01:19:22,350 --> 01:19:25,980
<font color="yellow">That tongue of yours is still senile after 900 years.</font>

885
01:19:27,680 --> 01:19:30,250
<font color="yellow">I will pull out your tongue first.</font>

886
01:19:30,650 --> 01:19:34,350
<font color="yellow">Then I will cut your body into pieces.</font>

887
01:19:37,550 --> 01:19:39,750
<font color="yellow">I will do it right now.</font>

888
01:20:02,480 --> 01:20:05,850
<font color="yellow">You, I or the 900 years.</font>

889
01:20:06,550 --> 01:20:09,950
<font color="yellow">You will not be able to hurt me with that sword of yours.</font>

890
01:20:19,580 --> 01:20:22,520
<font color="yellow">Did living as a goblin...</font>

891
01:20:23,150 --> 01:20:27,650
<font color="yellow">make you think that you actually became the almighty?</font>

892
01:20:35,050 --> 01:20:37,880
<font color="yellow">I will kill you no matter what, so do not worry.</font>

893
01:21:04,450 --> 01:21:09,250
<font color="yellow">The longing within makes one die of an unworthy death.</font>

894
01:21:09,450 --> 01:21:13,150
<font color="yellow">During the 20 years you spent rotting,</font>

895
01:21:13,150 --> 01:21:16,180
<font color="yellow">Yeo grew powerful...</font>

896
01:21:17,150 --> 01:21:18,380
<font color="yellow">beyond recognition.</font>

897
01:21:20,150 --> 01:21:21,980
<font color="yellow">If you speak of that name one more time...</font>

898
01:21:21,980 --> 01:21:26,580
<font color="yellow">Do you know the identity of the grim reaper by your side?</font>

899
01:21:26,580 --> 01:21:29,520
<font color="yellow">He's the man who gave you that sword...</font>

900
01:21:29,520 --> 01:21:33,610
<font color="yellow">and the one who pierced your heart with it.</font>

901
01:21:34,550 --> 01:21:36,980
<font color="yellow">That man is...</font>

902
01:21:38,020 --> 01:21:39,650
<font color="yellow">Wang Yeo.</font>

903
01:21:42,680 --> 01:21:43,710
<font color="yellow">Ludicrous.</font>

904
01:21:43,710 --> 01:21:46,810
<font color="yellow">Your foolish sister...</font>

905
01:21:46,810 --> 01:21:49,150
<font color="yellow">fell for him again in this life.</font>

906
01:21:51,750 --> 01:21:53,350
<font color="yellow">I pity you.</font>

907
01:21:55,750 --> 01:21:59,880
<font color="yellow">You will never have your revenge.</font>

908
01:22:10,710 --> 01:22:11,950
<font color="yellow">I heard you cried.</font>

909
01:22:13,310 --> 01:22:14,810
<font color="yellow">Why? Even I don't cry.</font>

910
01:22:14,810 --> 01:22:17,710
<font color="yellow">Who is the woman in the painting by the way?</font>

911
01:22:18,810 --> 01:22:21,880
<font color="yellow">I don't remember. I just feel.</font>

912
01:22:23,710 --> 01:22:25,780
<font color="yellow">I was just extremely sad.</font>

913
01:22:27,610 --> 01:22:29,280
<font color="yellow">My heart felt like it was breaking.</font>

914
01:22:31,280 --> 01:22:33,520
<font color="yellow">A super handsome uncle.</font>

915
01:22:38,310 --> 01:22:41,580
<font color="yellow">Have you seen a ring like this?</font>

916
01:24:31,310 --> 01:24:34,950
<font color="yellow">Is the grim reaper in your previous life?</font>

917
01:24:36,520 --> 01:24:39,080
<font color="yellow">- Have you seen him? - Excuse me.</font>

918
01:24:39,650 --> 01:24:42,810
<font color="yellow">What do you think you're doing in my restaurant?</font>

919
01:24:43,250 --> 01:24:46,580
<font color="yellow">Do you think I'm really Kim Sun because I remember my past life?</font>

920
01:24:46,580 --> 01:24:47,880
<font color="yellow">Is that man...</font>

921
01:24:50,780 --> 01:24:52,410
<font color="yellow">really Yeo?</font>

922
01:24:56,610 --> 01:24:59,750
<font color="yellow">- I have to go home. - I asked you a question.</font>

923
01:25:11,520 --> 01:25:12,780
<font color="yellow">Even in this life,</font>

924
01:25:14,610 --> 01:25:16,380
<font color="yellow">you are...</font>

925
01:25:18,210 --> 01:25:20,410
<font color="yellow">protecting that fool.</font>

926
01:25:55,410 --> 01:25:57,050
<font color="yellow">Was I?</font>

927
01:25:58,580 --> 01:26:02,010
<font color="yellow">Was I really Wang Yeo?</font>

928
01:26:03,450 --> 01:26:05,710
<font color="yellow">The feelings without memories...</font>

929
01:26:06,880 --> 01:26:09,480
<font color="yellow">Is that...</font>

930
01:26:10,650 --> 01:26:12,350
<font color="yellow">the punishment I gave myself...</font>

931
01:26:13,610 --> 01:26:15,580
<font color="yellow">so I won't forget who I was?</font>

932
01:26:51,650 --> 01:26:53,410
<font color="yellow">As expected,</font>

933
01:26:54,710 --> 01:26:57,380
<font color="yellow">it looks like I'm the worst memory.</font>

934
01:26:59,050 --> 01:27:00,880
<font color="yellow">To you...</font>

935
01:27:02,180 --> 01:27:05,510
<font color="yellow">and to Kim Shin, both.</font>

936
01:27:05,950 --> 01:27:07,710
<font color="yellow">You can hear me, can't you?</font>

937
01:27:12,280 --> 01:27:14,750
<font color="yellow">I hear yours, too.</font>

938
01:27:15,710 --> 01:27:17,450
<font color="yellow">I hear it very clearly.</font>

939
01:27:51,210 --> 01:27:53,280
<font color="yellow">Warrior Kim Shin...</font>

940
01:28:03,180 --> 01:28:05,180
<font color="yellow">greets you, Your Majesty.</font>

941
01:28:48,810 --> 01:28:52,210
<font color="yellow">(Goblin)</font>

942
01:28:56,210 --> 01:28:58,180
<font color="yellow">This royal garment...</font>

943
01:29:00,080 --> 01:29:02,180
<font color="yellow">is without an owner.</font>

944
01:29:07,210 --> 01:29:08,480
<font color="yellow">Maybe this is...</font>

945
01:29:13,110 --> 01:29:15,550
<font color="yellow">what you're looking for.</font>

946
01:29:23,410 --> 01:29:24,580
<font color="yellow">If so,</font>

947
01:29:28,150 --> 01:29:29,680
<font color="yellow">take it.</font>

948
01:30:00,680 --> 01:30:02,250
<font color="yellow">It is my royal decree.</font>

